Hi,

I finally found a solution..... If linux/i2c-dev.h cannot be used, I
define all the needed structures and constants in my own header
(src/lib/i2c-dev.h). That's not very elegant, but it should work...

Please do a cvs update, it should solve this problem.

Best regards,

Nicolas

