hi,
I'd like to report, that (g)ddccontrol works fine with my Samsung 193P 
Monitor and Club3D Radeon 9550 SE" graphics card under Debian "testing" 
with kernel 2.6.10.
all i had to do is create the /dev/i2c* entries, and copy the xml files 
from the 173P.

Thanks for some great work!

btw.: i don't really like the user interface gddccontrol, if you are not 
woking on it, i'd consider writing a nicer one myself...


Christian Schilling


