ACPI stuff, so start reading ACPI related kernel sources. This is pretty
easy in fact. There are already number of modules for ASUS, IBM, etc.
laptops, which could be used as a good sample. I've not checked acpi for
sometime already, but it's possible that it has support for SONY laptops
already.

Regards,
Oleg.

