Concerning your graphics card (i865G), there is some experimental support in
ddccontrol, but I never tested it (so I'm looking for testers). I you have some
time to test it (note you don't have to have a monitor supporting DDC/CI to test
it), please send me the output of "lspci -v -v" (run it as root).

Best regards,

Nicolas

