hello,

fglrx is not a framebuffer driver. it is the closed source X11 driver
from ATI. in fact it does not work properly together with framebuffer
divers.
see the "warning" in the documentation:
http://ddccontrol.sourceforge.net/doc/latest/apc.html#id2522151

also please notice this is the documentation of the lastest CVS version,
and does not apply to the currently released version.

-- 
