Hi,

I have succesfully got (g)ddccontrol working with my Samsung Syncmaster 970P.
I have included the monitors .xml file.

I have tested it with my Nvidia Geforce FX5600. For this I did not use the
recommended direct PCI memory access support, but I used the new
        Option "AllowDDCCI" "true"
in the 1.0.7676 nvidia drivers.

With this I have accelerated X and ddccontrol simultaneously!

Kind regards,

Martin Kalkman

