You're right, this was my output:

crw-r----- 1 root kmem  1, 1 2005-12-27 23:55 /dev/mem
-rwxr-xr-x 1 root root 20568 2005-12-03 15:27 /usr/bin/ddcpci

I've done a 'chmod u+s /usr/bin/ddcpci' and now it works fine..

Thank you very much !

mxt



